  Bruno, 66, could be seen smiling next to Arlene as they posed for a sweet picture together. “The song says we don’t talk about Bruno no no no,” she told her 40,300 Instagram followers, making a reference to the Disney film Encanto. “Well I talk about @brunotonioliofficial and haven’t stopped for many many many years. “Through ups and downs and twists and turns, secrets and adventures and stories to be told. “I saw him yesterday at a beautiful garden party held by dear friends and the gossip never stops.”   